text: Jacob Mulder (born 11 August 1995) is an Australian-born Irish cricketer. He made his Twenty20 International (T20I) debut against Hong Kong on 5 September 2016. He made his One Day International (ODI) debut against the United Arab Emirates on 4 March 2017. He made his first-class debut for Northern Knights in the 2017 Inter-Provincial Championship on 1 August 2017. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:Irish cricketers Category:Ireland One Day International cricketers Category:Ireland Twenty20 International cricketers Category:Cricketers from Perth, Western Australia Category:Northern Knights cricketers
